Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.80,0:00:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要对圣母玛利亚保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预备  开拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,读完这个之后  也就不难理解为何传闻白蔷薇是作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.00,0:00:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为故事舞台怎么看都是莉莉安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.50,0:00:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有  小令也读了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.10,0:00:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后她说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再插手这件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.20,0:00:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还说就当没读过这小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.40,0:00:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于传闻的事不想有任何牵扯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CUT OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.60,0:00:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.40,0:00:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  这附近开了家新的什锦煎饼店你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦  什锦煎饼店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是听说过  店主是个很风趣的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.80,0:00:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对对对  叫横山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.50,0:00:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫横山啊  你已经去过好几次了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.80,0:00:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每礼拜都去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.30,0:00:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不带我去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.20,0:00:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一煲起电话就停不下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.50,0:00:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人一直很多  要预约了才能去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.40,0:00:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那今天呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.40,0:01:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天  不是说了要预约嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.40,0:01:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下星期呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.70,0:01:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下星期没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.90,0:01:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便告诉我哪种好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.40,0:01:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荞麦面饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.20,0:01:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荞麦面饭  荞麦面和饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.30,0:01:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荞麦面和饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
